  "name": "genieops",
  "displayName": "GenieOps - The World's Most Powerful DevOps Extension",
  "description": "Type ONE sentence → Extension does ALL DevOps work automatically. AWS, GCP, Azure, Docker, Kubernetes, CI/CD, Auth, Payments - Everything via natural language with multi-AI orchestration.",
